uthern affiliates’ refusal to broadcast east side this explanation conveniently locates the bigotry behind the series’ cancellation with backward southern viewers rather than with the top brass of cbs but it doesn’t hold up to close scrutiny as edith efron pointed out in a  tv guide article east side  west side was dropped by no more affiliates in the south than in any other region of the country and ultimately only six percent of the potential viewing audience had the series blacked out in their areas it’s more likely that aubrey and his subordinates gave east side the axe because they were caught in a nowin situation they couldn’t allow the show to remain as openly liberal as it was for fear that the voluminous hate mail would scare off sponsors but they couldn’t eliminate the hotbutton elements of the series without endangering its critical cache and existing viewer loyalty had the show been a smash in the ratings its controversial nature would not have been an issue  kedrosky paul november   james earl jones on dr strangelove infectious greed retrieved    httpwwwimdbcomnamenmbio   actor george c scott dead at  the washington post associated press september   retrieved    show business meat parade time march   retrieved    mason wiley and damien bona february   inside oscar ballantine books isbn    mel gussow september   george c scott celebrated for patton role dies at  the new york times retrieved    david nusair december   the changeling reel film reviews retrieved    the beauty who tamed the beast people february   retrieved    george c scott tempering a terrible fire time march   retrieved february     ian curtis  appendix jesus myth or reality iuniverse p  isbn  george c scott american actor   during an interview on  minutes shortly before his death scott said he did not believe in god at all  nick ravo november   a snoozing bear upsets courtly connecticut politics the new york times retrieved    burt lancaster making gains in stroke therapy external linkse