eard by millions to decide their fate in this rough life and business called entertainment george like so many othet talented youths of our times comes from what today would be considered a large family consisting of nine george being the eight this alone for a poor family from pineland south carolina cause competition to find a place in the sun george scott wanted to sing and sing he does inspired by marvin gaye the late otis redding wilson pickett hung between these giants one has to find a way to be himself thats where george scott is now  getting into his own bag you record buyers will determine the fate of george scott but of course the disc jockies across the nation will have to first say to themselves let a man come in  let his talents be heard  heres george scott hope you enjoy his efforts  eddie ojay artist george scott produced by johnny brantley album design chromo photo chuck stewart maple records all platinum record co inc  w palisade ave englewood n j  available on track tapes and cassettes exclusively by ampex  customers who bought this item also bought jr monterose  the message brighter side of darkness  love jones the last poets  oh my people the last poets  this is madness new birth  coming together el combo nacional  esto si es boogaloo eddie harris  is it in phil moore iii leni groves  the afro latin soultet  afro brazil oba the nazty  i got to move pucho and his latin soul brothers  tough   join the mailing list copy  vinylcom george scott signed baseball w x gg inscription  boston red sox  mlb  modellscom home mlb boston red sox george scott signed baseball w x gg inscription previous next pin it george scott signed baseball w x gg inscription item  dsco steiner sports please select a size option please select a size option please select a size option  size qty  add to wishlist tell a friend description description red sox former first basemen george scott has personally handsigned this mlb baseball and inscribed it x ggduring his major league 