nd then cast again into a crescent form finally the crescent is ground and polished and then fired once more every inch of this piece contains amazing patterns with each individual layer of glass interacting with its neighbors reflected and transmitted light allow for many varied display opportunities limited edition of  shipping information need help your recently viewed items sign up for artful home emails sign up for artful home catalogs join artful rewards follow us visit the artful life blog artists sell your artwork through artful home quick links home art glass sculpture objects  decor art for the wall furniture  lighting apparel jewelry gifts site map my account customer sign in artist sign in trade professional sign in about us about artful home inspiration  community artist corner faq privacy  security legal contact us  toll free customer service become an artful home artist all contact info   artful home llc all rights reserved frank poems by george scott paperback  lulu all bookstore knowledge base shop frank poems by george scott paperback  pages this item has not been rated yet preview price  prints in  business days inspired by anne franks diaries these poems should give an insight into the secret annex add to cart embed ratings  reviews  product details ratings  reviews log in to review this item log in to rate this item you must be logged in to post a review please log in there are no reviews for the current version of this product refreshing  find reviews for previous versions there are no reviews for previous versions of this product refreshing to report this review as inappropriate please complete this short form email address  first name last name additional comments report product details copyright standard copyright license publisher george scott published january   language english pages  binding perfectbound paperback interior ink black  white weight  lbs dimensions inches  wide x  tall report this content to lulu  moderation of questionable